Type: Package
Package: messi
Title: Mediation Analysis with External Summary-Level Information on Total Effect
Version: 0.1.1
Description: Fits the hard constraint, soft constraint, and unconstrained models 
    in Boss et al. (2023) for mediation analyses with external summary-level 
    information on the total effect.
